  <synopsis><code mime="text/x-gjs">
function set_comment(group_name: String, key: String, comment: String): Boolean {
    // Gjs wrapper for g_key_file_set_comment()
}
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Places a comment above <code>key</code> from <code>group_name</code>.
If <code>key</code> is <code>null</code> then <code>comment</code> will be written above <code>group_name</code>.
If both <code>key</code> and <code>group_name</code>  are <code>null</code>, then <code>comment</code> will be
written above the first group in the file.</p>
  <p>Since 2.6</p>
